{"repo": {"timestamp": 1774604586000, "version": 20002, "name": "Bag", "icon": "icon.png", "address": "https://uxavia.github.io/fdroid-repo/repo", "description": "Official F-Droid repository for Bag \u2014 Bitcoin Portfolio Monitor for Android."}, "requests": {"install": [], "uninstall": []}, "apps": [{"categories": ["Money"], "suggestedVersionName": "1.2.0", "suggestedVersionCode": "18", "description": "Track your Bitcoin net worth in real time. Enter your BTC holdings, pick up to\n3 fiat currencies, and watch your portfolio value update alongside live price\ncharts and a DCA tracker.\n\nBitcoin-only. No altcoins. No ads. No accounts. No analytics. Your holdings\nnever leave your device.\n\nFEATURES\n\n* Net worth in up to 3 fiat currencies (USD, EUR, GBP and 50+ more)\n* Live BTC price charts - 1D / 1W / 1M / 1Y / ALL-time\n* DCA tracker with cost basis and P&L\n* Home screen widget with live price and net worth\n* Mempool fee estimates (sat/vB)\n* Sats / BTC display toggle\n* Dark and light theme\n\nPRO - one-time purchase, no subscription\n\n* Watch-only zpub wallet tracking (BIP84 / P2WPKH)\n* Tor routing via Orbot for full network privacy\n* Custom Esplora server support\n* Bitcoin Health Check - privacy score across all wallets\n* Sentinel: always-on balance monitoring with mempool alerts\n* Mempool fee alerts (above/below threshold)\n\nPRIVACY & SECURITY\n\nOnly address hashes ever reach the explorer - your zpub and balance stay\non-device. All network paths can be routed through Tor (Orbot required).\nNo phone-home, no telemetry, no third-party SDKs.\n\nOpen source: github.com/UXAVIA/bag", "issueTracker": "https://github.com/UXAVIA/bag/issues", "license": "GPL-3.0-only", "sourceCode": "https://github.com/UXAVIA/bag", "summary": "Bitcoin portfolio & net worth. No ads, no accounts.", "webSite": "https://bitbag.app", "added": 1774375128000, "packageName": "app.bitbag", "lastUpdated": 1774541694000, "localized": {"en-US": {"featureGraphic": "featureGraphic_a6mh